    "This media could consist of software, hardware, or a combination of the two.",
    "Dynamic assistive technology incorporates control apparatus, touch displays, and augmented and virtual reality applications, among other advanced technological computer gadgets that have evolved.",
    "These technologies can be used for both diagnosis and treatment.",
    "Pictures and images have piqued the interest of people with ASD (Charlop-Christy et al. 2002).",
    "They have proven to be efficient visual learners, and pictorial cards have been shown to be a successful teaching tool for children to learn how to perform daily tasks."
